title: RHOP: Sexual Healing, Mental Scarring
description:
The Real Housewives of Potomac is wrapping up, and so we've got an episode of odds and ends: Ashley trying to be intimate with Michael (yikes), Gizelle finally addressing her emotional coldness, and Wendy doing a photo shoot. Good times!

Be sure to join us for our 10th Anniversary tour here:

https://www.watchwhatcrappens.com/10th-anniversary-hunky-dory-tour/
